70210/extras/b4418c48b42b06c56eeb95fde963ce02.mp4?t=1697570186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>TURN BASED COMBAT<br>amazin' George 2 adds Turn based battles as a new game mechanic.<br><br>A BIG WORLD<br>The world of Felina, the world of cat dreams is a big one and will take hours of enjoyable turn based RPG gameplay to explore.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/138c5eff301e2107542b11c7b8932ccf.poster.avif?t=1697570186\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/138c5eff301e2107542b11c7b8932ccf.webm?t=1697570186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/138c5eff301e2107542b11c7b8932ccf.mp4?t=1697570186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>ROLE-PLAYING AT ITS FINEST<br>A mixture of familiar RPG elements, featuring dozens of locations to explore, diverse 3D characters with cute animation and secrets to find<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/595e9a8cd1918248ddfd4a5c9188d134.poster.avif?t=1697570186\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/595e9a8cd1918248ddfd4a5c9188d134.webm?t=1697570186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870210/extras/595e9a8cd1918248ddfd4a5c9188d134.mp4?t=1697570186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A POETIC STORY<br>-A charming story with rhymes!<br><br><strong>For more information on the Spacefarer Card Game, visit </strong>",
